- ğŸ§¾ Extracts invoice data from PDF
- ğŸŒ Retrieves exchange rates from the Bulgarian National Bank (BNB)
- ğŸ’¬ Converts total amount into Bulgarian words
- ğŸ§  Auto-fills a Word template with supplier and client data
- âœ… No database required â€“ works with `suppliers.xlsx`

